                            <comment id="14266218" author="gpetracek" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 15:07:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;deltaspike isn&apos;t responsible to handle events -&amp;gt; please file a weld-issue (about events and custom scopes)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;just fyi:&lt;br/&gt;
it works fine e.g. with tomee and wildfly&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14266227" author="nliechti" created="Tue, 6 Jan 2015 15:12:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Ok, thank you for the very quick response&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="14301358" author="jharting" created="Mon, 2 Feb 2015 15:04:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Partially a Weld bug because it calls Context.get(bean, null). Partially a DS bug as it always returns null on such a call.&lt;/p&gt;

